{"hb37aacaagdfc9g4992g807cg61729d8e709b": ["*Even with your keen eyesight, the hole below you soon plummets into an abyss of impossible darkness.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "3d8c4cc9-a30d-e44a-2d60-dab4d63098db"], "h7dac8cc8g91e8g47fegacd3gbc66ddf131a7": ["Looking into the hole, you see only darkness. It's impossible to tell how deep it goes by sight alone", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "3d8c4cc9-a30d-e44a-2d60-dab4d63098db"], "h57b62bdcgeed1g4506gbb20g92dd7441b66c": ["Hellooo?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "e1674d11-7742-1440-1118-72357b094245"], "h607c79abg1a6eg46f8gafafgc6cf39b53ca1": ["*Your call echoes as it plunges downward, before gradually fading away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "ddcdb95b-758a-cad2-5033-0f6e0978c77c"], "h4bfb2c3fg454dg48c7ga286g561a2c3620ca": ["*Growl.*", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "8c4e4a9b-41ed-4c55-a048-12a42e6c5a7b"], "hd6c5c3ddg0b6eg47fag8292g5304a8770321": ["<i>Quiet. </i>Or your meat will fill my belly.", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "17b1c90b-4b5a-4ad6-b5aa-74698e184eca"], "h8ebca20agef2dg4940g8477g38037c6a4a58": ["Apologies. Didn't mean to disturb... whatever you are.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "7c64917a-a9ca-d33f-9021-4fef5f474a06"], "hf0c00ee6g147fg437eg9ba5g4e8dbb446259": ["You disturb me still. Enough - away from here.", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "df3ca606-2502-92a8-59c5-2aaa4a23ca37"], "h4288dd24ga094g4496gbf09g9e15cac1bb69": ["Come up here and try it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "15baab70-de40-7a60-c5fb-65798adcd7c8"], "h351ca6d3g738fg49acga84dg448ab0c5a48d": ["Stupid. You won't last long here, noisy flesh-bag.", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "8d2ea87f-d609-db76-57f5-3387bf57220c"], "ha4f2dda0g01bbg4367g824bg0356faced596": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "114220dd-8364-f075-ce60-c28ce1a1301f"], "h89b99d8ag312cg4e13g86b6g7f85e6574ab9": ["<i>Listen and stare into the hole.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "822b60ad-b5eb-5284-e710-bc5bd9bb15cc"], "hc1a9b16cg7ea9g42ebgb100g0757fa77b4cd": ["*Faint sounds echo against unseen stone. Nothing discernible by eye or ear.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "f84c537b-df27-50ea-28dc-ea9fc3437b07"], "h06882f15g7a29g48e2g875ag4b18e76c982e": ["*The hole offers only pitch-black nothingness.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "ffd016cf-14e1-f8c2-c6e5-9b03d3576f2a"], "h38c87430g0a53g4944g83f6gf05212e45277": ["HellooooOH!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "72545e31-11ed-4a9b-8b09-73a284659e5c"], "h05d8fce4g9cc5g4093gb838g44108f85c350": ["*Roar!*", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "d10adc35-d73c-5f61-0dfa-714e764738ff"], "h0eefa51fgd3f0g464fga90fgd28cea648db8": ["I warned you, fleshbag. You'd better run.", "c286da16-eabe-4bac-acd1-3e9ee1bee510", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_DeepHole.html", "b9616c6d-9f38-a3c9-2602-802565c4112b"]}